```c
if (s_controller.door_closed) {
    if (input.pressure_kpa < CONTROLLER_PRESSURE_LOW_THRESHOLD) {  // 0 < 40, TRUE!
        // Low pressure: compress and close vent
        ...
    }
}
```

So it would think we have low pressure (0 < 40) and turn on the compressor! That's the bug!

